<header class="app-page-head"><div><p class="eyebrow">Direkter Vergleich</p><h1>Produktduell</h1><p>Wähle nicht das allgemein Beste — wähle deins.</p></div><nav class="dimension-tabs"><a href="<?=u('/app/battles?type=taste')?>">Geschmack</a><a href="<?=u('/app/battles?type=value')?>">Preis-Leistung</a><a href="<?=u('/app/battles?type=movie_night')?>">Filmabend</a><a href="<?=u('/app/battles?type=buy_again')?>">Wiederkauf</a></nav></header><?php if(!$battle):?><div class="empty-state"><h2>Zwei Bewertungen fehlen.</h2><p>Für ein Duell braucht SnackQuest mindestens zwei bekannte Snacks.</p><a class="button" href="<?=u('/app/scan')?>">Snack scannen</a></div><?php else:?><form method="post" action="<?=u('/app/battles/decide')?>" class="battle-stage"><?=$csrf?><input type="hidden" name="session_id" value="<?=e($battle['session_id'])?>"><input type="hidden" name="left" value="<?=e($battle['left']['product_key'])?>"><input type="hidden" name="right" value="<?=e($battle['right']['product_key'])?>"><input type="hidden" name="reason" value="<?=e($dimension)?>"><?php foreach(['left','right'] as $side):$item=$battle[$side];?><button type="submit" name="winner" value="<?=e($item['product_key'])?>" class="battle-card"><span class="battle-side"><?=$side==='left'?'A':'B'?></span><?php if(product_img($item['image_url']??'')):?><img src="<?=e(product_img($item['image_url']))?>" alt=""><?php else:?><span class="image-fallback">▦</span><?php endif;?><p><?=e($item['brand'])?></p><h2><?=e($item['product_name'])?></h2><strong><?=e($item['overall_rating'])?>/10</strong><em>Dieses wählen</em></button><?php endforeach;?><span class="versus">VS</span></form><?php endif;?><section class="rankings"><p class="eyebrow">Elo-Ranking · <?=e($dimension)?></p><h2>Deine Rangliste</h2><?php if(!$rankings):?><p>Noch keine Duelle in dieser Kategorie.</p><?php else:?><ol><?php foreach($rankings as $index=>$rank):?><li><b><?=str_pad((string)($index+1),2,'0',STR_PAD_LEFT)?></b><span><?=e($rank['product_name'])?><small><?=e($rank['match_count'])?> Duelle</small></span><strong><?=number_format((float)$rank['score'],0,',','.')?></strong></li><?php endforeach;?></ol><?php endif;?></section>
